title: Harry Potter
description: Orphaned hero of the plot whose ultimate destiny lies in a climactic battle with the evil Lord Voldemort.

title: Severus Snape
description: Potions teacher whose loyalty to Dumbledore and The Hogwarts School is in constant doubt -- until the final chapter.

title: Voldemort
description: Harry's arch-enemy in the ultimate battle agsint evil, AKA Tom Riddle, 'The Dark Lord', 'He-Who-Must-Not-Be-Named'

title: Hermony
description: The main heroine who transforms from one of the brightest and most righteous characters to one of the most gritty, brave and rebellious.

title: Ron Wizly
description: Harry's best friend and the story's major comic relief

title: Draco Malfoy
description: - Son of the evil Lucius Malfoy and Harry's arch-enemy at Hogwarts.

title: Bellatrix
description: Crazily wicked minion of Lord Voldemort and one of the first female Death Eaters introduced into the story.

title: Dumbeldor
description: Wise, powerful head of Hogwarts and Harry's main mentor.Harry Potter - Orphaned hero of the plot whose ultimate destiny lies in a climactic battle with the evil Lord Voldemort.

title: Siruis Black
description: Harry's surrogate father figure and Askaban prison escapee who later gives his life to help Harry lead the fight against Lord Voldemort.

title: Hagrid
description: Harry's friend and confidant, a lovable half-man half-giant who is Hogwart's school custodian and, later, Care of Magical Creatures teacher.

title: Navil Longbottom
description: Bumbling, absent-minded friend to Harry who later evolves into a major leader in Dumbledore's Army.

title: Peter Pettegriew
description: Friend of Dumbledore who comes out of retirement from fighting criminal wizards (which explains his prosthetic eye and wooden leg) to join Hogwarts in the final battle.

title: Luna Lovegood
description: Harry's illogical, loony and loveable school friend often described as the 'anti-Hermione.'

title: Professor Lupin
description: Hogwart's Defense Against the Dark Arts teacher who teams with Sirius Black to help Harry lead the charge against Lord Voldemort

title: Dolores Umbradge
description: In the final chapters appointed the 'High Inquisitor' at Hogwarts, and earning a place in children's literature as one of the most hated villains of all time.
